
# Privacy Policy

**CMHelpline** ("we", "our", or "us") is a mobile application designed to help users report and manage daily grievances and issues they face in their surroundings.

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the CMHelpline mobile app.

---

## Information Collection and Use

The app may collect and store certain information provided by the user for the purpose of grievance submission and resolution. This may include:

- Name
- Phone number
- Grievance details (text, category, etc.)
- Call logs (only if initiated through the app)

This information is **not shared with any third parties** and is used solely for providing support and managing the reported issues.

---

## Permissions

CMHelpline may request access to:

- **Phone/Call**: To allow users to make calls directly from within the app.
- **Internet**: To submit grievance data to the app's backend server.
- **Location (optional)**: To help identify the location of a grievance if shared by the user.

We do not access or use these permissions for any other purpose.

---

## Data Retention

User data submitted through the app is retained only as long as necessary to process and manage the grievance. It is stored securely and handled with care.

---

## Security

We value your trust in providing your personal information, and we strive to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

---

## Third-Party Services

CMHelpline does **not** use third-party analytics or advertising SDKs. All data remains between the user and our private servers.

---

## Children's Privacy

CMHelpline does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of 13. If we discover such data has been provided, it will be deleted immediately.

---

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

This policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage users to review the privacy policy periodically.

---

